justification: The class `TenantServiceImpl` contains multiple fields related to various configurations and services like `TenantMapper`, `WorkflowInstanceMapper`, `ScheduleMapper`, `UserMapper`, `QueueService`, `StorageOperator`, `K8sNamespaceUserMapper`, `MetricsCleanUpService`, and `SessionService`. These fields are part of the domain of tenant management and related operations. Extracting these fields into a separate class can encapsulate tenant management responsibilities and improve modularity.
